 2020-03982020-05-30,  GAC,  ,  , 
ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the United Nations Democratic Republic of the Congo Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the UNITED NATIONS DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO REGULATIONS in order to (1) fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council set out in Resolutions 1807 (2008), 2293 (2016), and 2478 (2019); and (2) address miscellaneous amendments requested by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
